Wrap your form in `KeyboardAvoidingView`:

```jsx
import { KeyboardAvoidingView, Platform } from 'react-native';

<KeyboardAvoidingView
  style={{ flex: 1 }}
  behavior={Platform.OS === 'ios' ? 'padding' : 'height'}
>
  {/* form content */}
</KeyboardAvoidingView>
```

- `behavior` determines how the view adjusts: `'padding'` adds padding, `'position'` moves the view, `'height'` (Android) adjusts height.
- Often used inside a `ScrollView` for forms.
